                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 21va: Donation note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 21va: ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘወሀብዋ፡ ካህናቲሁ፡ ለሚካኤል፡ ለአራእሮ፡ ደቂቀ፡ ተስፋ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ርእሰ፡ ሃይማኖት። ወአቡሆሙ፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ። ወለጸሐፊሁ፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡ ወኢትርስእዎሙ፡ በጊዜ፡ ጸሎትክሙ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። ዘሰረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Rubrication has been executed later. Rubricated words are often written only in parts (e.g. ማርያ instead of ማርያም or ሚካ instead of ሚካኤል. &#xD;
- Spaces for rubricated names and passages are left unfilled: fols. 20ra, 44va, 54vb.&#xD;
- Long passages omitted in the text are written in the margins: fols. 56v, 66va, 67ra.&#xD;
- Erasures marked with (crossed) lines: fols. 29va, 33va, 42ra or in a frame: fol. 39rb. &#xD;
- Erroneously written word crossed out: fol. 11ra.</item>
                     </list>
